text: For the 7th time @FedEx @FedExHelp delivered my package to the wrong address. I’ve called twice 2complain & nothing. Only happens with them, I receive things from #ups  #usps #amazon without problems; yesterday my new iPhone went to a neighbor who thank God knew me and called me!

@stevecordonr @stevecordonr Hello, this is Joe. I do apologize on behalf of Fedex for this delivery (mis) issue. This is not the experience we want to provide. Please DM @Fedexhelp recipient name, address w/ zip code, tracking number, phone number, and email address. 
https://t.co/7vnSkvqx3r

@stevecordonr @stevecordonr Hi, thank you for the tweet. I will review and respond when I receive your information. Thank you.
~joe
